  "comment": "ADJ continues to push the boundaries of LED technology with the Inno Beam LED, a compact intelligent Moving Head with a bright 80W LED source which produces a tight 6-degree beam projecting 8 colors plus white. The Inno Beam LED is lightweight and small in size. It has a Pan/Tilt Inversion mode that makes the heads produce contrasting movements.The Inno Beam LED has 5 selectable dimming curves, a high speed shutter and has a low power draw of 129W at maximum",
